The globe has gone mobile and today, it's not enough to simply bring your web assets to different handsets. Nope, you need to innovate for the mobile and to do so you need to create brand new user experiences that matter to your users, citizens, and members. Let's talk about a few ways to create new mobile apps through Open Innovation and Crowdosourcing competitions and why this way, is a great way forward.

